Model: A complete description of the current state of the universe
Object: Player, NPC, Room, Item
Event: Something that happens

Model: map
    Player: object
    Objects: list of objects
    Events: list of events

Object: map
    Descriptor: string
    Inventory: list of objects
    State machine: map
        States: map
            keyword -> string
        Transitions: map (key = keyword, value = map (key = keyword, value = keyword))
        Transitions: map
            keyword -> map
                keyword -> map
                    Target: keyword
                    Events: list of events
        Current: keyword

Event: map
    Descriptor: string
    Scope: fn
    Effect: string
